@Descr
In some cases it is possible to replace an LLL over the rationals by floating
point calculations: The result might involve rounding errors, but it is easy
to check whether relations found are actually genuine.
@Manual
@Ref
@Rem
This project makes only sense once a floating point arithmetic is available.
